@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor

actor "Waze CCP" as WazeCCP
actor "API User" as APIUser

participant "waze-data-download\nLambda" as DownloadLambda
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "waze-data-process\nLambda" as ProcessLambda
participant "Specialized Processing\nLambdas" as SpecializedLambdas
participant "Aurora PostgreSQL" as Database
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "waze-data-api\nLambda" as APILambda

DownloadLambda -> WazeCCP: Fetch data periodically
DownloadLambda -> S3: Store raw JSON data
S3 -> SNS: Trigger event
SNS -> SQS: Enqueue message
SQS -> ProcessLambda: Trigger processing
ProcessLambda -> S3: Retrieve raw data
ProcessLambda -> SpecializedLambdas: Distribute processing tasks
SpecializedLambdas -> Database: Store processed data
ProcessLambda -> SNS: Send processing status

APIUser -> APIGateway: Request data
APIGateway -> APILambda: Forward request
APILambda -> Database: Query data
Database --> APILambda: Return results
APILambda --> APIGateway: Send response
APIGateway --> APIUser: Deliver data

@enduml